OL,4,G1800FSpace 1999
OL,5,     GHumans from another planet,
OL,6,     Gfrozen for 300 years, are
OL,7,     Grecovered and revived.
OL,8,G1905FDanger Man
OL,9,     GA foreign senator is murdered in
OL,10,     Gthe presence of his blind
OL,11,     Grelative, Josetta. Rioting ensues
OL,12,     Gdue to a rumor that the American
OL,13,     Ggovernment was behind the
OL,14,     Gkilling, and secret agent John
OL,15,     GDrake is sent in.
