OL,4,G1935FDanger Man
OL,5,     GJohn Drake visits the Arabian
OL,6,     Gcoast to investigate illegal
OL,7,     Gslave trading. Disguised as a
OL,8,     Gslave trader himself, his
OL,9,     Gquestions meet with strong
OL,10,     Gresistance from both locals and
OL,11,     Gan Englishman.
OL,12,G2005FHallelujah!
OL,13,     GCaptain Emily Ridley has been
OL,14,     Gasked to retire from her position
OL,15,     Gin the Salvation Army but she
OL,16,     Grefuses. Now the Army must decide
OL,17,     Gwhat to do with this overbearing
OL,18,     Gwoman who relentlessly targets
OL,19,     Gsinners.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
